{"title":"解决 Heroku-cli 无法登陆","date":"2020-10-17T14:11:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2020年10月17日","L":"2020/10/17","MM-DD":"10-17"},"thumbnail":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/idkzr/static@master/imgs/herokuclilogin/cover.jpg","color":"#111","link":"posts/herokuclilogin","comments":true,"tags":["Heroku"],"categories":["瞎折腾"],"updated":"2020-10-17T14:11:00.000Z","content":"<p>在折腾 heroku 部署 OLAINDEX 时，使用 <code>heroku login</code> 但出现报错</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"> ›   Warning: login is not a heroku command.</span><br><span class=\"line\">Did you mean join? [y&#x2F;n]: y</span><br><span class=\"line\"> ›   Error: Missing required flag:</span><br><span class=\"line\"> ›    -a, --app APP  app to run command against</span><br><span class=\"line\"> ›   See more help with --help</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>随即便尝试使用<code>heroku login -i</code>但依旧是无法登陆</p>\n<p>于是便去看了看 help ，找到了解决方法。</p>\n<h3 id=\"1.获取-api-key\">1.获取 API Key<a title=\"#1.获取-api-key\" href=\"#1.获取-api-key\"></a></h3>\n<p>登陆 Heroku 后，前往 <a href=\"https://dashboard.heroku.com/account\" target=\"_blank\">Account settings</a> 页<br>\n找到<strong>API</strong>选项，点击 <strong>Reveal</strong> 复制 API Key</p>\n<h3 id=\"2.新建-.netrc\">2.新建 .netrc<a title=\"#2.新建-.netrc\" href=\"#2.新建-.netrc\"></a></h3>\n<p>Linux：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">touch ~&#x2F;.netrc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>Windows：找到环境变量目录新建：<code>.netrc</code> 文件</p>\n<h3 id=\"3.编辑-.netrc\">3.编辑 .netrc<a title=\"#3.编辑-.netrc\" href=\"#3.编辑-.netrc\"></a></h3>\n<p>使用vi/vim等编辑器编辑 <code>~/.netrc</code><br>\n输入如下内容：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">machine api.heroku.com</span><br><span class=\"line\">  login #heroku绑定的邮箱</span><br><span class=\"line\">  password #你的API Key</span><br><span class=\"line\">machine git.heroku.com</span><br><span class=\"line\">  login #heroku绑定的邮箱</span><br><span class=\"line\">  password #你的API Key</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>随后就可以尝试进行操作了233</p>\n<p>Enjoy !</p>\n","prev":{"title":"Heroku部署安装Typecho","link":"posts/typechoonheroku"},"next":{"title":"小米MIX 2S System分区扩容","link":"posts/mix2skr"},"plink":"https://blog.zr.ci/posts/herokuclilogin/","toc":[{"id":"1.获取-api-key","title":"1.获取 API Key","index":"1"},{"id":"2.新建-.netrc","title":"2.新建 .netrc","index":"2"},{"id":"3.编辑-.netrc","title":"3.编辑 .netrc","index":"3"}],"copyright":{"author":"箴扰","link":"<a href=\"https://blog.zr.ci/posts/herokuclilogin/\" title=\"解决 Heroku-cli 无法登陆\">https://blog.zr.ci/posts/herokuclilogin/</a>","license":"本博客所有文章除特别声明外，均采用(<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">CC BY-NC-SA 4.0</a>)许可协议，转载请注明来源<a href=\"https://blog.zr.ci\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">箴扰</a>！"}}